  <summary date="2019-06-27T14:25:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Coordinated Overdose and Drug Epidemic Response to the Emergency Declaration Act or the CODE RED Act

This bill establishes a series of requirements for the Office of National Drug Control Policy relating to the administration of drug control grants, including the creation of a tracking system, performance metrics, application standardization, and a centralized electronic portal for such grants.</summary>
